s; money transfers; and value-added services, as well as portfolio investment schemes. The company's business banking services include normal and premium accounts, SIB merchant plus, and trader smart current accounts; working capital, long term, non-fund based, supply chain, and SIB commercial vehicle loans; international finance; and merchant acquiring services. It operates through a network of branches and ATMs/CRMs. The South Indian Bank Limited was incorporated in 1929 and is headquartered in Thrissur, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 9355, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Peruvemba Ramachandran Seshadri B.E.", "age": 62, "title": "MD, CEO & Director", "yearBorn": 1963, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 32499000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Dolphy  Jose", "age": 56, "title": "Whole-time Executive Director", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 8912714, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Vinod  Francis", "age": 45, "title": "GM & CFO", "yearBorn": 1980, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Anto George T.", "title": "Chief Operating Officer", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. A.  Sony", "title": "Senior GM & Chief Information Officer", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Chithra  H. F.C.A.", "age": 56, "title": "Senior GM & Chief Compliance Officer", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 2217272, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. T. M. Mohan", "title": "GM & Head of Legal", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Nandakumar  G.", "title": "Senior GM, Head of Internal Audit & Chief of Internal Vigilance", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. K.